content: Hello! How can I assist you today?
Hey I am just quickly checking the transcription capabilities.
Great! I'm ready to help with that. Go ahead and speak, and I'll provide a transcription of our conversation.
Cool, I'm just checking whether the speech interaction speed is affected because you haven't transcribed what I'm saying.
Understood. The speech interaction speed should remain consistent whether I'm transcribing or not. Your feedback on how it goes is welcome.
